---
title: Pepper Jam Pork Tenderloin plus a Kale & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: We looked below the Mason-Dixon line for inspiration and came up with pork tenderloin smothered in a lush pan sauce. The key to the sauce is red pepper jam, which adds a tangy, sweet-savory flavor while sour cream adds a touch of indulgence. Joining the party is a tangle of sauteed kale with roasted sweet potatoes and onions. With a meal so plentiful and delicious, who can resist all this Southern charm?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pepper-jam-pork-tenderloin-3f52d56d.jpg
